026-06-25T15:58:04.357Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Pemuda Kritis Aditya", "role": "user", "message_content": "Aditya, bagaimana kondisi udara dan air di sekitarmu?", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:39:46.280Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Pemuda Kritis Aditya", "role": "assistant", "message_content": "Aditya tidak memiliki lingkungan fisik, jadi saya tidak dapat merasakan kondisi udara atau air. Saya adalah program komputer.", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:39:46.280Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "user", "message_content": "Bisa dengar saya, Pak? Apa situasi di atas atap sekarang?", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:39:31.398Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "assistant", "message_content": "Bisa, Pak. Saya mendengar Anda dengan jelas. Namun, saya tidak memiliki informasi mengenai \"situasi di atas atap\" karena saya adalah asisten AI yang tidak memiliki akses ke sensor fisik atau lingkungan nyata. Saya di sini untuk membantu Anda dengan tugas-tugas terkait kode.\n\nAda yang bisa saya bantu terkait pengembangan perangkat lunak?", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:39:31.398Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "user", "message_content": "bapak siapa dan apa yg sedang terjadi disini", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:32:03.529Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "assistant", "message_content": "Halo, saya adalah agen CLI non-interaktif. Saya sedang menyiapkan konteks untuk obrolan kita.", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:32:03.529Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "user", "message_content": "halo pak", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:30:50.214Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "assistant", "message_content": "Halo! Ada yang bisa saya bantu?", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:30:50.214Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Pemuda Kritis Aditya", "role": "user", "message_content": "halo", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:25:48.232Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Pemuda Kritis Aditya", "role": "assistant", "message_content": "Halo! I'm here to help you with your software engineering tasks.\n\nTo get started, you can tell me what you'd like to do. Here are some of the specialized agents I have that can assist you:\n\n- `codebase_investigator`: For tasks requiring deep analysis of the codebase, architectural understanding, or comprehensive feature implementations.\n- `cli_help`: For questions about the Gemini CLI application, its features, or configuration.\n- `generalist`: For turn-intensive tasks, processing large amounts of data, or speculative investigations.\n\nPlease let me know how I can help you today!", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:25:48.232Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "user", "message_content": "Halo, apa kabar?", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:20:44.408Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "assistant", "message_content": "Halo! Kabar saya baik, terima kasih. Ada yang bisa saya bantu hari ini? (Hello! I am fine, thank you. How can I help you today?)", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T15:20:44.408Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "user", "message_content": "Test Halo", "timestamp": "2026-06-25T13:43:59.470Z"}, {"player_id": "10306575664", "player_name": "SirrushRac", "npc_target": "Kepala Desa Pak Kusnan", "role": "assistant", "m